Dental De Care is one of those rare finds - a conveniently located, fairly priced, full-service dental practice distinguished by the caliber of its surgeons and overall quality of service.

Facilities (Rated 3.5/5): Occupying the entire ground floor of a residence, the surgery’s independent facilities – which include a Reception, Patient Waiting Area, 3 Consultation Rooms, X-Ray facilities, and Bathroom were clean, well maintained and provided for a safe and welcoming environment. The patient pool (based on my visibility) generally drew from a broad cross-section of Bangalorean society – with students, young working professionals, tourists, married couples, families and Grandparents in equal measure. 

Appointments and Payments (Rated 4/5): Appointments and bookings are handled over the phone, or in-person, and are digitally recorded with a complimentary text message reminder of your appointment conveniently delivered to your mobile phone 24-hours prior. Time slots were generally always available to fit my schedule and perhaps more importantly - appointments made, were appointments kept – with waiting times rarely more than 5 minutes. Payments are accepted via Cash or Charge with receipts provided for all transactions. 

Services Provided (Rated 5/5): A full-service Dental practice, ‘Dental De Care’ provides a complete breadth of services covering both essential care and cosmetic solutions. Most common procedures – such as cleanings and fillings - require but a single visit to complete, with more complex procedures such as root canal + crown combinations generally requiring two sessions. 

Dental Practitioners (Rated 5/5): In perhaps the most important facet of care – the caliber of its surgeons - ‘Dental De Care’ truly shines. The practice provides access to a full-service suite of highly accomplished dental surgeons and specialists, to include Orthodontists, Prosthodontists, Periodontists, Pedodontists, Endodontists and Oral-Maxillo Facial Surgeons (many UK / US trained, and with 20+ years of experience). Furthermore, a patient’s care is guided not by general surgeon availability, but importantly, by the specialist best suited to handling a particular procedure. Personally, based on my initial experience with the surgery, I decided to take care of some long-overdue dental work – throughout which, I was always treated by a specialist in the field, and always felt like I was in safe and experienced  hands. Special thanks to Dr. K.M Pramod, Dr. Prithvi and Dr. Rozina. 

Quality of Service (Rated 5/5): In Dr. K. M. Pramod, I found an accomplished medical professional - patient, caring, with sharp diagnostic skills and thoroughly uncompromising on the overall quality of service provided. Overseeing and guiding a patient’s overall care, Dr. Pramod provides a wealth of information on treatment options and typically detailed 2-3 solutions with varying emphasis on speed, durability, cosmetic viability, cost etc. Procedures are then handled either by Dr. Pramod (for Orthodontics) or specifically by a specialist in the particular field. Frequent consultations between specialists ensured treatment plans remained on-time and on-budget. 

Overall (Rated 4.5/5): In today’s world of impersonal assembly-line medicine, ‘Dental De Care’ is a rare find – a socially responsible practice focused on long term patient health. It’s rare to find folks who will consciously steer you away from a more expensive treatment for one far more affordable, practical and better focused on a patient’s particular need – but this occurred on more than one occasion during the course of my treatment. It was little surprise then to learn that over 95% of patients at the practice came from personal referrals and long-term repeat customers. I found myself impressed by the surgeons, extremely pleased with the both the high quality of work as well as overall service, and simply cannot recommend ‘Dental De Care’ highly enough !!

I have been visiting Dr. Pramod for more than 10+ years. He has helped me with implants, root canal and other dental procedures. Both his father and he has been giving me many tips for dental hygiene. He has been very friendly and supportive to me and my family. We have immense trust in his ability to resolve our dental issues in the best possible way even if it means getting other expert doctors from outside.  I take this opportunity  to thank him, visiting doctors and support staff in his clinic  for all their services done for me and my family.

The Doctors are very friendly. They explained in detail what was best for a patient like me😊. I love the way how doctors attended and cared for my problems or my situation and even the cost was affordable. In addition to this, I love the clinic ambiance and it’s very much hygiene. Iam looking forward to go to the clinic again very soon as I have other dental issues to fix, which I couldn’t do before because of a personal situation at that time. 
I highly recommend this clinic for others too💕

I am going Orthodontic treatment with Dr. Pramod.  ** ** *** **** ****** * **** ****** *** *** ****** ********** 

I did a thorough research before I started my treatment with Dr. Pramod. I went to many doctors for teeth alignment but all have suggested that they have to remove some of my teeth for teeth alignment. But Dr. Pramod was the one who suggested me that it can be done without removing any of my teeth. 

Now the result is in front of me. Its almost 8 months now and I can see the difference. My all teeth are aligned and now in proper shape.

He is a very polite, humble and understand your problem thoroughly before recommending any solution.

** ** *** **** *** ****  ***** ***** **

I visited Dr Pramod for tooth alignment a year back. He clearly explained the differences between traditional braces and Invisalign.  After the consultation and weighing the pros and cos of each treatment, I went ahead with Invisalign. I was quite anxious at the beginning and had a lot of questions about the process. Dr Pramod was very patient in answering all my queries and that gave me the confidence to go ahead with it.

Invisalign has worked well for me. It was a hassle-free treatment. The aligners were comfortable and removable when eating and cleaning. While I was wearing the braces, they were hardly noticeable and near to invisible. I saw visible results in the first two months itself and in 6 months my teeth were 90 percent straight. 

Dr Pramod and his team are very diligent, and they helped me ensure that I was wearing the aligners, following the guidelines, and keeping the appointments. Overall, I had a good experience throughout the treatment!

I have consulted Dr. Pramod (& Dr. Medha) multiple times in Dec (2019) & Jan & have been Highly Satisfied with the quality of service. There were multiple teeth fillings which were needed for my son & wife which were attended to very well. After that I needed to get a new Denture made - the fitting of the new Denture was Perfect the first time round. Both Dr. Pramod & Dr. Medha took the time to explain in detail regarding dental hygiene & other issues. Would highly recommend this Doctor. Also the clinic is ultra modern & very clean. Loved it !!

review_reply.reply_text:
Hello Mr Sridhar,

I’m saddened to hear, for not having the best experience at my Dental Practice. My team and I strive very hard to give the best treatment to the extent possible. 
It is very unfortunate that you did not have that experience.

Some procedures need more than usual time, wether its for root canal treatment or crown. we schedule repeated appointments to ensure high quality and successful treatment. You confirmed over the phone, you were comfortable with new crown this time, which we replaced it free of cost. 

At any point of time , i did not mislead you, nor overcharged / recharged you for extra appointments, nor left you half way  of the treatment.

And i assure you every instrument under goes three cycles of different sterilisation, because of which, the instruments loose their lustre over a period of time. 

If we can be of further assistance, please do not hesitate to contact us back. I will personally ensure that you will have the best experience.
Regards
Dr Pramod
